{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_11_01_short",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 サキュバスってなんですか！？ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n……それ、何を読んでいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ good work today.\n…What is that you’re reading?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、星見プロのアイドルを起用した恋愛ゲーム\n『もし恋』は、瑠依も知ってるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ it's about the romance game featuring Hoshimi Pro idols.\nYou know about \"Moshi-Koi‚\" right‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 246.53088249999922,
          "startTime": 6.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "その制作会社から、新しい企画が届いたんだけど……\nそうだ。良かったら瑠依の意見も聞かせてくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The production company sent over a new proposal…\nRight. If you don't mind‚ could I hear your thoughts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9666659673,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9266.6666667,
          "startTime": 26.233332634
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "新しい企画ですか。もちろんです、拝見させて下さい\nえーと……ファンと一緒に作るゲーム？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new proposal. Of course‚ let me take a look.\nLet's see… A game made together with fans?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.633332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……ファンの投票でゲームのジャンルやユニット名\nそれに衣装も決めていくんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… So the fans vote to decide the genre‚ unit name‚\nand even the costumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.133332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの意見がこんなに反映されるなんて……\n凄く、面白い企画だと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think the fans' opinions are reflected this much…\nI think it's a very interesting project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、俺もいい企画だと思う。この企画が本決まりに\nなったら、瑠依にも出演を相談させてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I agree. Once this project is officially greenlit‚\nI'd like to talk to you about appearing in it‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1238008254,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6342.867685100004,
          "startTime": 54.4666685105
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、気が早いですよ。もう少し資料を\n読み込んでみないと……これがゲームのジャンルですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you're getting ahead of yourself. I need to\nread through the materials more… so this is the genre list.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのテーマ候補は……えーっと、まずは\n『本格？　どたばた！！　サスペンス！？！？』ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The theme candidates are… Let's see‚ first is\n\"Authentic? Slapstick!! Suspense!?!?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333351772,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}